Ganga v508r6 (GangaLHCb-24-11)
******************************

1) Minor bug fixes

2) Addition of automatic XML summary parsing and merging upon job completion. Some of the more
common usages of the XML summary (implemented from GangaUtils) have been included automatically. In
addition the summary.xml file is also returned with the job so the user can parse it as they wish
post running. XML summary data populates the new metadata attribute of a job which also dynamically
extends the syntax of the job object as in the example below.

In[1]: j=Job(...)
In[2]: j.submit()

...

In[3]: j.metadata
Out[3]: { 'xmldatafiles': "{'full':
set(['LFN:/lhcb/LHCb/Collision11/DIMUON.DST/00012368/0000/00012368_00000355_1.dimuon.dst'])}", 
          'xmldatanumbers': "{'full': 1}", 
          'lumi': '1.60795849653 +- 0.0562785473787, 
          'events': "{'output': 0, 'input': 364573L}", 
          'xmlskippedfiles': 'set([])' 
         }

The job syntax is dynamically updated with the metadata item such that with the above metadata one
can call

In[4]: j.lumi
Out[4]: 1.60795849653 +- 0.0562785473787

